## CẦN BỔ SUNG: 10 Frameworks thiếu data

Chỉ Budget Warrior có `chapter_template`, `transitions`, `pacing`. 10 cái còn lại thiếu:

| Framework | `chapter_template` cần | `transitions` cần |
|---|---|---|
| Contrarian Takedown | Leader claim → Challenger data → Verdict | Dimension kết → next dimension tease |
| Underdog Champion | Myth → Data surprise → Reassessment | "But what about X?" bridge |
| High-Stakes Scenario | Scenario setup → Test → Survival verdict | Escalating stakes |
| Legacy Justification | Heritage → Modern test → Endurance proof | Era progression |
| Tier List | Tier placement → Evidence → Tier verdict | Tier jump announcement |
| Myth Buster | Myth statement → Evidence → Truth reveal | "Next myth is even worse..." |
| Evolution Timeline | Previous gen → New gen → Delta measurement | Generation leap |
| Head-to-Head Duel | Round announce → Product A → Product B → Winner | Round result → next round |
| Golden Age Legacy | Nostalgia → Modern test → Still relevant? | Time period progression |
| Industry Shakeup | Announcement → Analysis → Disruption score | Impact escalation |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Mỗi framework cần bổ sung vào JSON: `chapter_template`, `transitions`, `pacing`.
> Có thể generate từ logic framework hoặc phân tích từ sample scripts.

